            <bug_when>2012-03-24 06:57:03 +0000</bug_when>
            <thetext>Right now TextAnalyzer as well as list.jsp (anything else?) use the JVM&apos;s default charset for all projects if they can&apos;t determine it automatically (which is probably the most common case) - on many *x it defaults to ISO8859-1, on others to UTF-8 etc. ...

So a per project setting of the charset to use for reading text files is desirable.</thetext>
